        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>普通攻擊</color>\n造成1點 <color=#ffe699>岩元素傷害</color> 。"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "璇璣屏",
        "title": "璇璣屏",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/2a1c2baa706dfc49f86033be36f170e9_214705509797190541.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素戰技</color>\n造成2點 <color=#ffe699>岩元素傷害</color> ，生成 <color=#ffffff>璇璣屏</color> 。\n<color=#ffffff>璇璣屏</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n<color=#ffffff>我方出戰角色受到至少為2的傷害時：</color> 抵消1點傷害。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "天權崩玉",
        "title": "天權崩玉",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/02/181140897/55dfd3944aa4091c2684c17412739558_7473569786414452379.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "<color=#ffd780>元素爆發</color>\n造成6點 <color=#ffe699>岩元素傷害</color> ；如果 <color=#ffffff>璇璣屏</color> 在場，就使此傷害+2。\n<color=#ffffff>璇璣屏</color>\n<color=#ffd780>出戰狀態</color>\n<color=#ffffff>我方出戰角色受到至少為2的傷害時：</color> 抵消1點傷害。\n<color=#ffffff>可用次數：2</color>"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
      {
        "key": "岩元素傷害",
        "title": "岩元素傷害",
        "iconUrl": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/01/23/84496276/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_4554621203137607680.png",
        "desc": [
          {
            "type": "RichText",
            "text": "和已附著的元素發生元素反應：\n【 <color=#ffe699>岩元素</color> + <color=#99ffff>冰元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>結晶（冰）</color> ：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）\n【 <color=#ffe699>岩元素</color> + <color=#80c0ff>水元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>結晶（水）</color> ：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）\n【 <color=#ffe699>岩元素</color> + <color=#ff9999>火元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>結晶（火）</color> ：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）\n【 <color=#ffe699>岩元素</color> + <color=#ffacff>雷元素</color> 】 <color=#ffffff>結晶（雷）</color> ：本傷害+1，我方出戰角色獲得1點護盾（可疉加，最多2點）"
          }
        ],
        "attributes": []
      },
